node.text: Seek what sets your soul on fire 🗺
We’re walking in a winter wonderland ❄️ #frozenlake

The concept of time is weird and the present moment is the only that truly matters and yes, we can also change and grow and be whatever we want at any moment. But with a new calendar year having come about, I figure it’s the perfect time to start thinking forward to the new year ahead. I am looking forward to manifesting the reality I want and seeing dreams I’ve had come true and I am even looking forward to the struggles that I know are bound to come up along the way. I’m looking forward to become stronger and sharing the love I have to offer this world, as  well as being open to accept the love the world has to offer me back. Let’s start it off with a simple smile. #happynewyear 💫

did you think I was a city
big enough for a weekend getaway?
I am the town surrounding it
the one you've never heard of
but always pass through
there are no neon lights here.

#rupikaur 🌎🌻
